article.description: — Javion Hamlet posted 16 points as North Texas topped Southern Miss 65-49 on Friday night.
article.headline: Hamlet lifts North Texas over Southern Miss 65-49
article.linkText: Hamlet lifts North Texas over Southern Miss 65-49
article.story: HATTIESBURG, Miss. -- — Javion Hamlet posted 16 points as North Texas topped Southern Miss 65-49 on Friday night. Zachary Simmons had seven rebounds for North Texas (11-6, 7-2 Conference USA). Abou Ousmane also had seven rebounds. Justin Johnson and Tyler Stevenson had nine points apiece for the Golden Eagles (7-13, 3-10), who have now lost seven games in a row. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
